song_lyrics: Shobhe shobhe rasikvar chhel re, Hari Dharmakuvar sukhkārī... ṭek°
Rājat shirpar jarakasī pagīyā, bankī kalangī laṭakel re... Hari° 1
Gajarā shekhar hār bājubandha, guchchha gulābī dharel re... Hari° 2
Kesar tilak manohar kīno, kunḍaḷ nang jaḍel re... Hari° 3
Kṛuṣhṇānand kahe Nāth nirantar, urmā vaso alabel re... Hari° 4
title: Shobhe shobhe rasikvar chhel re
